            <!-- Slide 15: Summary -->
            <div class="slide">
                <div class="slide-content">
                    <img src="https://cdn-icons-png.flaticon.com/512/2964/2964517.png" alt="Operative Dentistry Icon" class="operative-icon">
                    <h1>Key Takeaways</h1>
                    <ul style="text-align: left;">
                        <li>Proper preparation is foundation for success</li>
                        <li>Material selection should match clinical needs</li>
                        <li>Adhesion protocols vary by system</li>
                        <li>Matrix systems enable proper contacts</li>
                        <li>Incremental technique reduces stress</li>
                        <li>Finishing/polishing improves longevity</li>
                        <li>New materials expand treatment options</li>
